{"article_id":"yMavsGsQjijmltSA","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"poster= '' http : //v. .com/images/1155968404/201908/3469/1155968404_6077313192001_6077313591001-vs.jpg","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"? pubId=1155968404 '' trade","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Trump claims","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"China asked for renewed trade talks","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"BIARRITZ , France -","depth":3},{"id":5,"text":"President Donald Trump claimed on Monday","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"that Chinese officials are prepared to return to the negotiating table ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"signaling","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"there may be a path to a potential détente in his tit-for-tat trade war with Beijing .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"\" China called last night our top trade people","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"and said ,","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"' Let ' s get back to the table. '","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"They have been hurt very badly ,","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"but they understand","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"this is the right thing","depth":13},{"id":15,"text":"to do","depth":13},{"id":16,"text":"and I have great respect for it , \"","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"Trump told reporters during a bilateral meeting with Egyptian President Abdel Fattah el-Sisi on the sidelines of the G-7 summit .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"\" They want to make a deal , \"","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"Trump continued .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"\" That ' s a great thing . \"","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Chinese Foreign Ministry spokesperson Geng Shuang appeared to dispute Trump 's claim","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"that such phone conversations had taken place .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"\" I am not aware of the phone calls over the weekend","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"you mentioned , \"","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"he said in response to a question at a Monday press briefing .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"\" What I can say is that the trade differences should be solved through dialogue and consultation. \"","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"Playbook newsletter","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"Sign up today","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"to receive the # 1-rated newsletter in politics","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Email Sign Up","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"By signing up","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"you agree to receive email newsletters or alerts from .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"You can unsubscribe at any time .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"Treasury Secretary Steve Mnuchin told reporters","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"that Chinese Vice Premier Liu He had called for talks to resume","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"when Trump pressed him for details during a bilateral meeting later in the afternoon with the Indian prime minister .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"It was not immediately clear , however ,","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"if Mnuchin was referring to a phone call","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"Liu made to U.S. officials or his comments at a technology conference earlier in the day .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"Trump reiterated Monday","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"that China wants to reach a deal on trade \" very badly , \"","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"repeating claims","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"that the country ' s economy is bending under the pressure of U.S. tariffs .","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"\" I think","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"they want to make a deal .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"I 'm not sure","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"they have a choice .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"And I do n't say that as a threat , \"","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"he said in a joint news conference with French President Emmanuel Macron .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"But the confusion continued","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"over whether a call between U.S. and Chinese officials actually took place","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"and if so ,","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"when it occurred .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"In addition , no date for an expected round of high-level talks in September has been announced .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"`` We 've had many calls , ''","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"Trump said Monday ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"when pressed by a reporter on the issue .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"`` Secretary Mnuchin is here ,","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"and [ he 's ] had many calls over the last 24 hours , but certainly over the last 48 hours .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"We 've had many calls , not just one .","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"These are high-level calls .","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"They want to make a deal .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"And by the way , I think","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"a deal is going to be made . ''","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"Macron said","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"Trump , in private meetings with other G-7 leaders , \" clearly showed us his willingness","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"to arrive at an agreement \" with China .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"\" What 's bad for the world economy is uncertainty","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"and the quicker an agreement is arrived at ,","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"the quicker that uncertainty will dissipate , \"","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"Macron said .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"\" That 's what we discussed yesterday","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"and that 's the American president 's wish. \"","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"Trump ' s whiplash-inducing comments come","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"just 24 hours after White House officials","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"- seeking to clarify a statement","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"the president made","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"about having second thoughts on his escalating trade war -","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"said","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"his only \" regret \" was that he didn ' t raise tariffs further on Chinese imports .","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"That claim followed Trump ' s announcement Friday","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"that he planned to increase existing tariffs on $ 250 billion of Chinese goods , from 25 percent to 30 percent , and to hike a new round of tariffs on another $ 300 billion in Chinese exports from 10 percent to 15 percent .","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"Asked about the mixed signals","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"coming out of the White House ,","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"Trump shrugged","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"and said :","depth":15},{"id":87,"text":"`` Sorry , it 's the way","depth":17},{"id":88,"text":"I negotiate ...","depth":17},{"id":89,"text":"It 's done very well for me over the years","depth":17},{"id":90,"text":"and it 's doing better for the country . ''","depth":17},{"id":91,"text":"Then , he again blamed his predecessors","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"for allowing China to run up a huge trade surplus with the United States","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"and failing to take strong steps","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"to deal with unfair trade practices and the theft of U.S. intellectual property .","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"Adding to the confusion , Trump projected an air of indifference over the past several days","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"about whether a deal would be reached","depth":14},{"id":97,"text":"because of the tariff revenue","depth":14},{"id":98,"text":"now being collected on Chinese imports .","depth":14},{"id":99,"text":"\" I ' m getting a lot of money in tariffs .","depth":15},{"id":100,"text":"It ' s coming in by the billions , \"","depth":15},{"id":101,"text":"Trump told reporters here Sunday morning ,","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"adding","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"that he believes","depth":15},{"id":104,"text":"China wants \" to make a deal much more","depth":16},{"id":105,"text":"than I do . \"","depth":16},{"id":106,"text":"The president also opened the door to","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"using his executive powers","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"to declare a national emergency with respect to China ' s trade practices ,","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"saying , however ,","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"that he currently has no plans","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"to do so .","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"\" It has become unquestionably clear that the administration ' s tariff war against China is politically motivated .","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"What Washington wants from its largest trade partner is for it to be content to play second fiddle","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"and meekly do","depth":14},{"id":115,"text":"as it demands , \"","depth":14},{"id":116,"text":"China Daily , a state-owned newspaper , wrote in an editorial on Sunday .","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"By Monday , however , both U.S. and Chinese officials appeared open to resuming talks on trade","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"- that is ,","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"as long as such discussions remain \" calm , \"","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"Liu said at a conference in China .","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"\" We think","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"an escalation of the trade war is against the interest of China , the U.S. and the entire world , \"","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"said Liu ,","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"who is China ' s top trade negotiator .","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"Trump said","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"he appreciated Liu 's call","depth":14},{"id":127,"text":"for discussions to remain calm","depth":14},{"id":128,"text":"and said","depth":14},{"id":129,"text":"he felt the same way ,","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"even though it was the United States that ratcheted up tensions in recent weeks","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"by announcing a new round of tariff increases .","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"`` I thought","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"it was a beautiful statement , ''","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"Trump said in response to Liu .","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"`` I thought","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"it indicated a lot . ''","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"Liu added","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"that China \" will strive to protect the integrity of industrial chains , \" an element of the trade dispute","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"that Trump mentioned earlier in the day .","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"\" They have supply chains","depth":14},{"id":141,"text":"that are unbelievably intricate","depth":14},{"id":142,"text":"and people are leaving","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"and they are going to other countries ,","depth":15},{"id":144,"text":"including the United States , by the way , \"","depth":15},{"id":145,"text":"Trump said .","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"Many household U.S. companies have supply chains in China ,","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"where major disruptions have occurred","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"as a result of the ongoing trade war .","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"On Monday , Trump suggested","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"the U.S. is \" going to get a lot of \" production back","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"if his administration reaches a deal with the Chinese .","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"Liu ,","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"who never mentioned","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"whether phone conversations took place ,","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"Beijing is \" willing to solve the problem through consultation and cooperation with a calm attitude . \"","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"Trump has used the G-7 summit","depth":8},{"id":158,"text":"to advance his trade agenda in the face of skeptical European allies ,","depth":8},{"id":159,"text":"including by announcing Sunday","depth":8},{"id":160,"text":"that he and Japan had reached an agreement \" in principle \" on trade .","depth":8},{"id":161,"text":"He and British Prime Minister Boris Johnson also discussed the broad contours of a bilateral trade deal","depth":8},{"id":162,"text":"once the United Kingdom leaves the European Union .","depth":8},{"id":163,"text":"Johnson has set a deadline of October for his nation 's departure from the European Union ,","depth":8},{"id":164,"text":"which","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"he ' s repeatedly said","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"will occur with or without a deal with the EU .","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"With hours to go","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"before the three-day summit concludes","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"and he returns to Washington ,","depth":8},{"id":170,"text":"Trump said","depth":8},{"id":171,"text":"the U.S. is \" in a stronger position now","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"to do a deal","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"- a fair deal for everyone \" with China .","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"\" Anything ' s possible , \"","depth":10},{"id":175,"text":"Trump said Monday .","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"\" We ' re having very meaningful talks .","depth":7},{"id":177,"text":"Much more meaningful that at any time ,","depth":8},{"id":178,"text":"I would think . \"","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":357,"left":182,"right":356,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":182,"left":180,"right":181,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":180,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":181,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":356,"left":211,"right":355,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":211,"left":4,"right":210,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":210,"left":203,"right":209,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":203,"left":197,"right":202,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":197,"left":185,"right":196,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":183,"right":184,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":184,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":196,"left":193,"right":195,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":193,"left":187,"right":192,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearit